NovaBay is a biopharmaceutical company focusing on the commercialization of prescription Avenova® for the eye care market.




About Us













  





Avenova is the essential part of any lid and lash hygiene regimen.




Learn About Our Products













  





NovaBay is addressing the large, unmet therapeutic needs of the global anti-infective market with its pure, proprietary, stable form of hypochlorous acid called Neutrox®.




