^ "NovaBay Avenova has a low toxicity but kills eyelid bacteria in dry eye or blepharitis patients.". 
^ "Treatment of Acute Necrotizing Fasciitis Using Negative Pressure Wound Therapy and Adjunctive NeutroPhase Irrigation Under the Foam". 
^ "NNFF Names NovaBay's (NBY) NeutroPhase Its Official 'Flesh-Eating Disease' Wound Cleanser". 
