^ Steven E. F. Brown (February 26, 2014). "NovaBay Pharmaceuticals makes deal for flesh-eating bacteria cleanser". San Francisco Business Times. Retrieved June 19, 2014. 
^ "NovaBay Pharmaceuticals and Virbac Enter Into a Collaboration and License Agreement for Animal Health". 



